{"tid":190714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屠房外為豬隻發聲 素食者：豬與狗只是外表不同（2）","createTime":"2017-04-07T09:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T15:02:27.000Z","uid":76930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19e4eba355c0094ffccddc3f1a54208718fc04be","tid":190714,"uid":76930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"CD-ROM曬成個post，未留得切言就1001。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAnyway 開呢個post有兩個目的：<br />\n一.滿足Add比人撚嘅欲望<br />\n二.比露荀回答其他問題<br />\n<br />\n希望可以滿足兩位同其他Ching嘅須要。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f0a9f8a92f3713d0a751ebc3f36bf35797a370","tid":190714,"uid":76930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:24:26.000Z","msg":"最後問題<br />\n<blockquote>#1000瑕疵豆蔲 &bull; 8h<br />\n又係你<br />\n今次好似食返藥<br />\n點解唔關環保事? 其實關咩事食素又關你咩事?<br />\n唔正常果個似係你囉 齋同素都唔識分<br />\n唔好獻醜啦好唔好?<br />\n點解食素都俾你阿滋阿左俾人屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不嬲都講，做任何事都要睇佢「動機」<br />\n為環保，為個人健康，為其他嘢而食素咁有咩問題?<br />\n因為都會有正面影響而唔係負面</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一直覺得齋等如果D佛教偽肉，口齋心不齋。個人認為好虛偽，又多色素，所以寧願係菜心落多D鹽、係通菜落多D辣椒萛。請問我觀念有冇錯?定係應該開放D?<br />\n瑕疵豆蔲Ching"},{"pid":"fb893f52e28ed8ac0aee26e4f0245366681188fa","tid":190714,"uid":18310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"我唔算素食，但而家只食海產"},{"pid":"e22a1be54fea8489a9fa804c24feadd64c058652","tid":190714,"uid":76930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔算素食，但而家只食海產</blockquote><br />\n又係一個問題，魚唔會放屁，咁又會唔會縮短地球壽命？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05135c47c5bab90671eb047c7b43dd52a576e821","tid":190714,"uid":76930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:39:44.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d0f81d30767afd172a3f897edb2851b89798f1c1","tid":190714,"uid":76930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:53:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pish</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a676e52f7095bb0cdfce3efdbbf3f97bd9f9ac7b","tid":190714,"uid":76930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T11:27:13.000Z","msg":"接住果條問題：<br />\n<blockquote>#993Addgjknvfffdd &bull; 12h<br />\nEarth formed around 4.54 billion years ago <br />\n<br />\n我今次就唔用地球hp論黎同你個懵撚講<br />\n我用西瓜舉個例<br />\n假設小明有一個西瓜 如果一般人食 一星期就食曬<br />\n但小明諗諗下先發覺慳d食其實可以兩個星期先食完<br />\n咁即係西瓜落到小明手中原本正常壽命係一星期但小明慳住食令到個西瓜多左一星期壽命存在囉 明未呀柒頭?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Le個係資源<br />\n但係地球能源源於太陽同史前生物<br />\n地球冇左石油 生物<br />\n重係唔係地球<br />\n如果閣下承認冥古代嘅地球係地球<br />\n為何不承認資源用盡嘅地球係地球?</span><br />\n<br />\n再假設個西瓜完全唔食放三星期就會熟到爛唔適合食用 咁呢個西瓜已經唔係西瓜變左垃圾啦 情況咪同地球表面被破壞 大氣層臭氧層穿曬地球唔再係地球 香港冇左一國兩制就唔係香港一樣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過依你既logic黎諗一定會話呢個西瓜即使熟到爛唔食得都仲係西瓜黎 因為佢入面仲有西瓜肉(你果d地核觀點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 你既logic係一架車冇左外殼得番副引擎都仲係一架車 一間屋冇左屋頂但仲有廳/廚房/廁所/房都仲算係一間屋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">NASA話臭氧層源於1 billion years ago<br />\n咁1 billion years ago以前嘅地球又係唔係地球?<br />\n如果係又點解不承認未來冇臭氧層嘅地球係地球呀?<br />\n<br />\n如果兩者皆否 請大師再為地球定義壽命</span><br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"be4ffb0e39c1ccf625fbe729bd2659c59302371c","tid":190714,"uid":76930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"之後果條:<br />\n#986露荀 &bull; 13h<br />\n<blockquote>你繼續咬文嚼字挑骨頭掩飾自己講過幾多on9觀點囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頭先都講左 會引用霍金係因為你唔承認&quot;人類可以破壞地球&quot; 所以我就搵左篇霍金認為人類可以破壞地球亦同時破壞緊地球因為溫室氣體同病菌問題既文章黎再次屌打你<br />\nHe argued that unstoppable developments in science and technology were likely to prove the biggest danger, adding that the human race may only be able to survive in colonies on other planets in the solar system.<br />\n唔識英文但又扮識想扮大袋拋人? 呢段既大綱係人類不停既科學同科技發展會帶黎最大既危機 人類如果要生存只可以去太陽系中其他星球生活<br />\n我問你 以家人類係咪不停發展緊科技同科學先? 當然係啦 所以咪就係同全篇文講緊既中旨一樣人類毀滅緊地球要生存就要搵第二個星球移民 但係未有能力移民去第二個星球時就要好好控制番地球既生態先<br />\n睇文唔係逐粒字睇架係睇大綱要明白成篇文既意思架小朋友 小學1,2年班已經教過架啦 屌你老未閱讀理解中同英都唔合格學人出黎辯論 笑大人個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出唔曬 delete咁d 順手幫你遮醜 益埋你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇在咁耐，唔明點解你成日屈人唔支持環保? 雖然人地比你撚，但係人地一直有話支持環保以保護人類文明喎。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14a94d565